pod is the smallest unit we can create in kubernetes.

Imperative Approach
==========================
kubectl run abipod1 --image=busybox

declarative approach:
==========================
```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: abipod1
spec:
  containers:
  - name: busybox
    image: busybox
    ports:
    - containerPort: 80
```

[!IMPORTANT]
 How can you edit a pod ?

